A user should be able to
  Shirts(name, source_url, has_many tags, has_many lessons)
    See their shirts
    See a specific shirt
    create a new shirt
    update a shirt
    delete a shirt
  Lessons(topic, info, has_many shirts)
    CRUD lessons

  Tags(name)
    Created when adding a shirt

# ========
URLS
GET /shirts
POST /shirts
GET /shirts/new
GET /shirts/:id
GET /shirts/:id/edit
PATCH /shirts/:id
DELETE/shirts/:id

shirts
-------
id, name source_url image_url

tags
------
id, name

classifications
----------
id, shirt_id, tag_id
